title: China stocks up 4% as focus switches to the Fed
text:
China stocks up 4% as focus switches to the Fed By Matt Clinch 2 hours ago ÓÅ± . View photo STR | AFP | Getty Images. Chinese investors recover their poise as we gear up for another bumper day of earnings and the Federal Reserve monetary policy meeting. 
Hello and welcome to Wednesday's Squawk Box Live . China's stock markets staged a late rally as we gear up for another bumper day of earnings and the conclusion of this month's Federal Reserve monetary policy meeting. 
Stay tuned for all the latest news comment and analysis.
